edu.ucla.sspace.graph.isomorphism
Interface State

All Known Implementing Classes:
TypedVF2State, VF2State
public interface State

An interface for representing the partial or complete state of an a attempted isomorphic mapping between two graphs. This interface exposes as set of common operations used by AbstractIsomorphismTester to detect isomorphism in a general manner while leaving the algorithm specifics isolated to a State implementation.
